<template>
    <button @click="$emit)" class='btnInForm'>
      {{label}}  
    </button>
  </template>
  
  
  <script>

  export default {
    name: 'BtnInForm',
      props: {
        label: {
          type: String,
          default: 'test',
        }
     }
  }
  </script>
  
  <style scoped>
    .btnInForm {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
  </style>
